hopobject.body: How do you know each other? lexapro or celexa for social anxiety On one of her days off, she decided to go to Jerusalem to see the Upper Room, where the Last Supper had taken place. What she found, she said, was a cave and a gun-toting Israeli soldier with a Brooklyn accent who, when she exclaimed that this couldn’t possibly be the site of the Last Supper, said: “What were you expecting, lady, a Renaissance table set for 13?”
